{"tid":1492050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實華記係咪臥底黎","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:29:06.000Z","uid":78238,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e54ef4011fd7bdd2216da22b9230714699238b71","tid":1492050,"uid":78238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"頭先屋企廢老係到睇華記條片<br />\n成班藍絲廢老係度圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n跟住聽到佢係到叫人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寧願睇美國報紙都唔好睇香港報紙</span></span> <br />\n（等廢老唔好睇紅報？）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見到連儂牆唔好搞，影底擺上網</span></span><br />\n（宣傳連儂牆？）<br />\n<br />\n見到示威者要講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「對唔住，我錯，走先」</span></span><br />\n（等少啲手足比藍絲襲擊？）<br />\n<br />\n加埋<br />\n<br />\n佢自己<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">衝出黎証明示威者無收錢</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190819/59946919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F59946919&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=9a6a2cf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F59946919&h=420f3776\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190819/59946919</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪幫緊我地？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcfdf7713a45a01d045144b303753af23f4020b","tid":1492050,"uid":2562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd